      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable driver at a great value? This car is in fair condition and ready to get you where you need to go! It shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking affordable transportation. It\u2019s a practical, hardworking vehicle with plenty of life left for its next owner!",
