    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in drivable shape. It suffers from a blown head gasket and a failing transmission that slips significantly in second gear. The exterior has extensive rust along the rocker panels and a cracked windshield, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and a non-functioning climate control system. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it will need to be towed from its current location.",
      "price": 3500.0,
