      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances reliability with comfort. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, showing only minor signs of use such as a few light stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the driver-side mirror housing. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all electronic features\u2014including the navigation and heated seats\u2014fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts smoothly, backed by a consistent service history. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a brake inspection, ensuring it is road-ready. It offers the peace of mind of a solid mechanical pedigree without the premium price tag of a showroom-floor model.",
